reviewText: Helpful principles  .  EE is whimsical , humble
This teaching is a move of God and is saving and strengthening marriages in Kenya, Trinidad and Tobago, Jamaica, Haiti and all over the USA.

Not only is the study very Scripture-centered, which is a rare commodity in today's religious landscape, but it also is extremely practical. Dr. Eggerichs brings the Scriptures down to the daily experiences of life in marriage. You definitely get the benefit of his years of counseling in this area. Amazing, challenging, right where you live. As a Pastor, I will definitely be using this in my church and for marriage counseling for years to come.
super fast delivery, nice kit. Easy to work with the books. we found it very helpful so far

Just as good if not better than the original conference DVd's ! This is great material to refresh and re-energize marriages of all kinds.  The teaching gets to the core of what really matters. I believe that every married couple, whether newlyweds or mature couples, has much to glean from this!
Content was great.  However, the DVD casing was very cheap and flimsy. The DVDs did not stay attached to the casing and were moving around in the case.

Great Product.  Great Packaging.  Great Price.  Great People to do Business with.

Mahalo Nui Loa (Hawai'ian: Thank You Very Much) for fulfilling your obligation in a glorious way.

Cheers ><>
